snippet.title: Strangers In The Land Of Turnabouts [BLIND] Part 1: I'm Just Albert
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty]

A defense attorney, Mr. Albert, sets out to prove a landlord didn't steal a car from one of his tenants. Nothing more, nothing less. A civil trial, of all things, from Mr. WithAMask... Should be a good time!

Case by DudeWithAMask! Play it here: http://www.aaonline.fr/player.php?trial_id=106832
